INSERT INTO
    ais_vessels_temp (
    mmsi,imo_number,call_sign,name,ship_width,ship_length,ship_type,eta,draught,destination
   )
SELECT
    *
FROM
    UNNEST(
        $1::INT[],$2::INT[],$3::TEXT[],$4::TEXT[],$5::INT[],$6::INT[],$7::INT[],$8::TIMESTAMPTZ[],$9::INT[],$10::TEXT[]
    )
        ON CONFLICT (mmsi) DO UPDATE SET imo_number = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.imo_number, ais_vessels_temp.imo_number),call_sign = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.call_sign, ais_vessels_temp.call_sign),name = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.name, ais_vessels_temp.name),ship_width = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.ship_width, ais_vessels_temp.ship_width),ship_length = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.ship_length, ais_vessels_temp.ship_length),ship_type = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.ship_type, ais_vessels_temp.ship_type),eta = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.eta, ais_vessels_temp.eta),draught = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.draught, ais_vessels_temp.draught),destination = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.destination, ais_vessels_temp.destination)
